In laravel table files are knows as migration

Default Migration File - users(database/migration)
Default Model - User(app/Models/User.php)

Custom
=========
Migration - Students
Model - Student

Migration - Employees 
Model - Employee

Convert Migration File into Table
===================================
CMD ==> php artisan migrate (******Craete Table)

What is Migration?
======================================
Model - Handle Database opertions (insert, delete, update). It is a class.
Migration is resposible for table management.
Note:-
Each migration has a corresponding model.

Users Table <------------> User Model
Students Table <------------> Student Model

Creating Custom Model and Migrations
========================================
CMD ==> php artisan make:model ModelName -m

Ex :
php artisan make:model Student -m

>> Student MODEL
>> students MIGRATION FILE (in this we define table columns)

CMD ==> php artisan migrate



